# Portfolio Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 🎨 PORTFOLIO REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define portfolio categories
   - [ ] Identify showcase projects
   - [ ] Plan visual hierarchy
   - [ ] Determine interactive elements
   - [ ] List required contact methods

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Touch interactions for gallery

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Project showcase grid/gallery
   - [ ] Project detail pages
   - [ ] About/Bio section
   - [ ] Skills/Services section
   - [ ] Contact form
   - [ ] Social media integration
   - [ ] Download resume option

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── portfolio/
│   │   ├── ProjectCard.tsx
│   │   ├── ProjectGrid.tsx
│   │   ├── ProjectDetail.tsx
│   │   └── Gallery.tsx
│   ├── about/
│   │   ├── Bio.tsx
│   │   └── Skills.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── ContactForm.tsx
│       └── SocialLinks.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── projects/
│   ├── about/
│   └── contact/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Design Patterns
1. **Visual Hierarchy**
   - Project thumbnails: 16:9 or 1:1 ratio
   - Typography scale: 1.618 ratio
   - Whitespace: minimum 24px between elements
   - Grid gaps: 16px-32px responsive

2. **Animation Guidelines**
   - Hover effects: 200-300ms duration
   - Page transitions: 400-500ms
   - Loading states: subtle pulse
   - Scroll animations: fade and slide

3. **Layout Principles**
   - Maximum width: 1440px
   - Project grid: 2-4 columns responsive
   - Gallery spacing: 5% margins
   - Consistent padding: 24px-48px responsive

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Image Optimization**
   - Lazy loading implementation
   - WebP format with fallbacks
   - Responsive image sizes
   - Thumbnail optimization

2. **Loading Speed**
   - Initial load: < 2s
   - Time to Interactive: < 3s
   - Image loading strategy
   - Progressive enhancement

3. **Animation Performance**
   - Use CSS transforms
   - RequestAnimationFrame for JS
   - Debounce scroll handlers
   - Optimize paint operations

## 🎨 Visual Requirements

1. **Image Presentation**
   - High-resolution display support
   - Color profile management
   - Lightbox functionality
   - Zoom capabilities

2. **Interactive Elements**
   - Smooth hover states
   - Click/touch feedback
   - Loading indicators
   - Transition effects

## 📱 Mobile-First Considerations

1. **Touch Interactions**
   - Swipe gestures for gallery
   - Touch-friendly navigation
   - Mobile-optimized lightbox
   - Tap targets: 44px minimum

2. **Content Adaptation**
   - Stack grid items
   - Simplified navigation
   - Optimized image sizes
   - Reduced animations

## 🔄 Implementation Process

1. **Setup Phase**
   - [ ] Project initialization
   - [ ] Image optimization pipeline
   - [ ] Animation library setup
   - [ ] Gallery component setup

2. **Development Phase**
   - [ ] Core layout implementation
   - [ ] Portfolio grid/gallery
   - [ ] Project detail pages
   - [ ] Interactive features

3. **Content Phase**
   - [ ] Project content upload
   - [ ] Image optimization
   - [ ] Meta descriptions
   - [ ] SEO optimization

4. **Testing Phase**
   - [ ] Performance testing
   - [ ] Mobile responsiveness
   - [ ] Animation smoothness
   - [ ] Image loading

## 📈 Analytics Integration

1. **Key Metrics**
   - Project view counts
   - Time on project pages
   - Contact form submissions
   - Download tracking

2. **Event Tracking**
   - Gallery interactions
   - Project clicks
   - Social media links
   - Resume downloads

## 🔍 Quality Assurance

1. **Visual Testing**
   - Cross-browser appearance
   - Responsive breakpoints
   - Animation performance
   - Image quality

2. **Performance Testing**
   - Lighthouse scores
   - Image load times
   - Animation FPS
   - Interactive response time

## 📝 Documentation Requirements

1. **Technical Documentation**
   - Setup guide
